{"tid":2159144,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"《搏屌》我屌hktvmall 屌光榮 屌渣哥","createTime":"2020-08-16T06:50:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T07:08:11.000Z","uid":45652,"like":13,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0bb0a5c28d1668069e7c70894bac6e47098286e7","tid":2159144,"uid":45652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T06:50:43.000Z","msg":"我屌hktvmall 賺錢但刻薄員工<br />\n屌光榮廁所屎塔開住但呃人話用黎做倉<br />\n屌渣哥假民主愛分化<br />\n都係想大家唔好再比市場帶導<br />\nMarketing愈叻唔代表愈要懲罰<br />\n好似潮食閣煮飯比監獄手足食<br />\n出哂奶力幫手足反而要告急？<br />\n分化起大台反而開分店？<br />\n大把黃店代替上面唔洗死攬某幾間<br />\n死攬果啲佢開一間附近黃店就執幾間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37fd32fc46294ddf5e816cca994ba6defc464144","tid":2159144,"uid":45652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T06:53:02.000Z","msg":"黃色經濟圈又名黃色茶記圈"},{"pid":"81f9d2d55ffa246229dff1291a559e159eb1bcf9","tid":2159144,"uid":2300,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T06:54:48.000Z","msg":"但永遠都係唔屌藍店<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f40bd3230681322fd020ae6b8728ec4e398d38d3","tid":2159144,"uid":45652,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"81f9d2d55ffa246229dff1291a559e159eb1bcf9","tid":2159144,"uid":2300,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T06:54:48.000Z","msg":"但永遠都係唔屌藍店<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T06:56:55.000Z","msg":"你食藍店？"},{"pid":"7f039e530b48a78d6087a88a2a2bb8d621c3ca83","tid":2159144,"uid":2300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f40bd3230681322fd020ae6b8728ec4e398d38d3","tid":2159144,"uid":45652,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"81f9d2d55ffa246229dff1291a559e159eb